review_body: First thing I love here, no need to register, doesn't need any information about us. We can join with our friends by using random code. That's I love lot. Simple and neat. Some suggestions: chat environment may be added in future. Create point table. Increase multiplayer. Draw options may be added.

Superb game but sometimes there comes an network issue in both the mobiles which we want to play ......but the app is superb and functions are also too good ..those who are installing this app no need to worry ....this app have safety too.but plzzzz check what's the network problem..

Very nice game to play...very well suited for playing with friends without any online payment...no chip...no payment required. you can play with your family and friends. Very nice. If you can add 6 players, it would be great.
If we receive call, the player gets dropped. Also no drop facility available. Sometimes the game doesn't open. Otherwise the app is very good
Good app, but need some improvement. Need drop option and more players options. Also, it keeps disconnecting, that must be improved.
No chat support for android. Connection time out after 30 seconds of screen time.
Presently the app is good and should add 6player option and teen patti should also be included in the app. Over all its a good app for rummy and for free multiplayer mode .
